title: Data Visualization 101
description: A simple (but still effective) visualization that demonstrates some of the principles of effectiveness in data visualization. Created with a unique combination of data cleaning, aggregation, and visualization tools.

title: An Investigation on Nutrition
description: A partner project investigating the effect of nutrition on people's percptions of health and our diet culture. Based on a dataset that scrapped thousands of online recipes to build a linear regression model to predict calories.

title: N-Gram Language Model
description: A direct approach to a language model that builds on the foundations of probability to create text based on a fixed size window of previous words.
